# Go standards

- Run `gofmt` on changed Go files; keep `go vet ./...` clean.
- Use table-driven tests where it reduces duplication.
- Avoid unnecessary global mutable state in library code under `internal/`.
- Keep `main` thin: wire flags and call `internal/server` (and later `internal/resp`); avoid large logic in `main.go`.
